          %h5 Volunteer
          %p Do you live in or near Salt Lake City? We need all the help we can get for various projects and events all of the time. Give us a call to find out how you can help!

        .col.m6.sl2
          %h5 Donate
          %p If you don't live in the area, or can't fit us into your schedule, a donation could be a great way to help out. By no means do we solicit donations for our own profit, but many refugees as much help as possible.


